{"tid":2357980,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解歐盟唔多怕中國要脅呢？","createTime":"2021-01-07T22:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T07:50:08.000Z","uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc608a035a1c572bde01817af544a7becc9fea74","tid":2357980,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:12:07.000Z","msg":"原因好簡單，軍事上影響唔到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國點勁都好，始終隔住太平洋同印度，同俄羅斯唔同，隨時殺入芬蘭東歐。歐盟肯 9up 兩句已經可以感恩了，國際戰線甚麼的都的歐洲除英國冇乜效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f57ef10546c337e60a8bafc7c3c06559594287","tid":2357980,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:15:24.000Z","msg":"連登囝成日笑歐盟軟弱乜乜物物，其實係人地本身都唔多想知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲想打乜鬼最強戰線，講成日見咁多議員都講唔中人地利害關係，唔幫你係道理，幫你係人情。歐洲對集中營可能仲有興趣，睇中國點對新疆再抄考返對難民"},{"pid":"fbaa82d070bd86770411a7a8112a2cd7c7bae62b","tid":2357980,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T22:18:26.000Z","msg":"重貼舊文☆<br />\n<br />\n歐美介入下的民主戰爭的失敗及背叛歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2338138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2338138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9461ac86f5b7b65438474c0ec0a94cf336c5c78","tid":2357980,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:26:39.000Z","msg":"歐盟已在崩潰邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbcb583d7ca668f4c3cf6e35b6042bad6dc7195","tid":2357980,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"自身內部四分五裂，仲邊有可能團結歐洲對抗中國"},{"pid":"b1a9a9436908d43f70dab2d12a36b4d4ad930d30","tid":2357980,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9461ac86f5b7b65438474c0ec0a94cf336c5c78","tid":2357980,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T21:26:39.000Z","msg":"歐盟已在崩潰邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/m